Here is the complete set of 13 hour episodes of the Carl Sagan's original 1980 series &quot;Cosmos&quot;, converted from AVI/XVID to Chromecast-compatilbe H264/AAC MP4 files. 

To make it easier to play some of my favorite TV series on Google Chromecast, I decided to batch convert my AVI files to more robust and efficient H264 encoded MP4 files. This is much better than jumping through hoops with problem-prone &quot;transcoding&quot;. Converted files are 50% smaller without any notable loss in quality.

